    "body": "I was unable to reproduce the issue or track down why this is happening. The problematic code is the following:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/4dda6d2505323df6c2899cb6a38179a63b0f3d95/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/FastBlocks/FastHeadersSyncFeed.cs#L723\r\n\r\nI would expect `TotalDifficulty >= Difficulty` to be an invariant but it looks that at some point, `TotalDifficulty` is less than `Difficulty`. Where exactly this invariant is broken is unknown, due to these being properties that get mutated in so many places (+50).",
